Module detection
Package fr.project.detection.classVisitor

Class MyClassVisitor

java.lang.Object
org.objectweb.asm.ClassVisitor
fr.project.detection.classVisitor.MyClassVisitor
public class MyClassVisitor
extends org.objectweb.asm.ClassVisitor
A visitor to visit a .class file. It contains observers that can react when the visitor detects some features. It also contains a list of nest-mates of the class and store them into a field. A MyClassVisitor object is linked to a .class file and cannot be linked to another .class file when the project Retro is running.
Author:
SIMONNOT Florent
